WEBVTT

00:00:00.280 --> 00:00:06.033
I was trying to show you all this beautiful little squirrel before I started.

00:00:06.034 --> 00:00:18.445
He's hungry; he's eating french fries. He grabbed that french fry and he's going up the tree.

00:00:18.446 --> 00:00:37.562
You see him up there? He's a fat thing; he likes french fries.

00:00:37.563 --> 00:00:47.882
God is so good. Don't you just love nature? I have a better angle. All right, let's see here.

00:00:47.883 --> 00:00:55.668
Well, we just came from Victory Church in Tulsa and we went to see John Bevere with my family.

00:00:55.669 --> 00:01:08.415
And you know, on the way to the church today, the Lord showed me that massive revival again and he spoke to me about being hungry.

00:01:08.416 --> 00:01:35.570
He said, 'Brandon, never lose your hunger for what's coming.'He said, 'You must remain hungry; keep yourself stirred up for what's coming, being filled with the Holy Spirit.'It's so vital to go and get in those rivers whenever you have a speaker come to your church like that.

00:01:35.571 --> 00:01:44.504
I've never visited Victory in Tulsa; we've always gone over to Collinsville.

00:01:44.505 --> 00:01:51.526
But when I was going over there, the Lord showed me the caps of the wells again and the great revival.

00:01:51.527 --> 00:02:00.698
He spoke to me and he said, 'Brandon, I'm going to use this church.'He's looking for people who will just say yes.

00:02:00.699 --> 00:02:18.799
He's looking for people because he said, 'Brandon, I'm running out of time.'There are so many ministers right now that he's tugging at their hearts; he's tugging at their heartstrings, saying, 'Will you be a vessel that will help me bring in the harvest?

00:02:18.800 --> 00:02:32.247
Will you be those people that God can use in this last outpouring?'There are so many people that if they just have a little bit of a check going, 'I don't know,'he's going to bypass you.

00:02:32.248 --> 00:02:41.576
He's out of time; he's not going to sit there and try to coerce you into being part of this revival.

00:02:41.577 --> 00:02:49.113
If you are a vessel that wants to be used in the revival, you're going to be used.

00:02:49.114 --> 00:02:55.966
I believe it's all hands on deck; this is an all-hands-on-deck type scenario.

00:02:55.967 --> 00:03:13.853
If your heart is hungry and thirsty for the Lord, get ready, because in this scenario, he is looking for those that seek him—they will find him. Those that knock, the door will be opened unto them.

00:03:13.855 --> 00:03:36.374
I'm telling you all, when I went into this church at Victory—and usually I steer away from megachurches a lot; I worked at one and I saw all the drama behind the scenes, you know, that's just my opinion—so Diana and I kind of gravitate towards smaller churches.

00:03:36.375 --> 00:03:48.182
But when we went in there, the presence of the Lord was so strong and the people going down to the altar worshipping the Father, it was genuine.

00:03:48.183 --> 00:03:55.034
You look for: is this a show? I always have my spiritual antennas up.

00:03:55.035 --> 00:03:58.759
When people say, 'Are you judging them?'No, I'm discerning.

00:03:58.760 --> 00:04:06.115
And I genuinely discerned a spiritual hunger in these people.

00:04:06.116 --> 00:04:22.596
The Lord showed me that it was about the Mabee Center and the glorious outpouring and the uncapping of the wells that were back in the 1950s.

00:04:22.597 --> 00:04:36.758
I told you, from Jack Coe to Oral Roberts to Kathryn Kuhlman to William Branham, to all the greats that used to walk in the healing movement and the revival—it was the same thing.

00:04:36.759 --> 00:04:45.272
I'm telling you, they barely touched a thimbleful of what God's about to do in these end times.

00:04:45.273 --> 00:04:50.892
We will finish this up, and he has called you for such a time as this.

00:04:50.893 --> 00:05:23.892
He saved the best for last; that's what he was showing me: 'Brandon, I've saved the best for last.'And right now, he said, 'I'm tugging at the people's hearts to see who is for me, who will go and preach the gospel to this final generation.'He said, 'Fan the flame of hunger; never lose the hunger for me.

00:05:23.893 --> 00:05:34.958
Keep me a priority in your life.'I just want to encourage you all to be excited about what God is about to do in this end-time army.

00:05:34.959 --> 00:05:56.097
Diana and I can see it; we both felt it. I said, 'My goodness, didn't you, babe?'It's amazing how hungry the people are.

00:05:56.098 --> 00:06:15.113
I really believe, tangibly, with Oral Roberts University being there and how hungry those kids are, you could see them there. Megan's handing in the to-go box.

00:06:15.114 --> 00:06:22.598
Bill Johnson is going to be there tonight and he's going to be preaching, and I've never heard him live before, so we're going to go listen.

00:06:22.599 --> 00:06:31.799
The old wells—so Bill Johnson's coming and he's going to preach three services, I believe.

00:06:31.800 --> 00:06:42.748
I've never heard him live before, so I thought, 'Well, let's go and check it out.'I guess he has Bethel Church out in California.

00:06:42.749 --> 00:06:54.083
I'm just hungry for y'all. I know what I've seen about the plague and the things that the Lord has told me about it.

00:06:54.084 --> 00:07:08.498
I made a video on it but I haven't released it. The Lord showed me more about this; I had an open-eyed vision about four days ago, and he showed me dates.

00:07:08.499 --> 00:07:25.359
I'm just keeping that to myself right now, just praying over it, because I don't want to be hasty in releasing something just because I see it.

00:07:25.360 --> 00:07:39.752
Because of how the platform has grown, I think it's wisdom to pray over things a lot more and not be so quick.

00:07:39.753 --> 00:07:44.758
Right now, he said, 'Fan the flame. Go on YouTube and fan the flame.

00:07:44.759 --> 00:07:51.451
Get people excited about what's coming—a major harvest of souls.'Look at all the things.

00:07:51.452 --> 00:08:03.119
In the first week of Trump being in office, all the change that is happening. Hasn't it been amazing, Diana?

00:08:03.120 --> 00:08:11.659
He's done more in the first week of his presidency than Joe Biden did in his whole four years. It's been incredible.

00:08:11.660 --> 00:08:37.237
Even with the Prince of Saudi Arabia—I started, I went, 'Oh my God, he's doing a deal with MBS.'He's like, 'I think we can make it a trillion-dollar deal.'It's just amazing to see the end times unfolding right in front of our faces.

00:08:37.238 --> 00:08:50.769
I believe we will see in the days ahead a great acceleration of Turkey helping out Syria.

00:08:50.770 --> 00:09:06.705
When I was praying, the Lord showed me that the Temple Mount, the Third Temple in Jerusalem, is about to be built.

00:09:06.706 --> 00:09:18.353
Trump will have a major part in bringing forth the peace accord with Saudi Arabia and these other nations, and we will see the Third Temple be built in a short amount of time.

00:09:18.354 --> 00:09:24.301
I'm not going to tell you when, but I'm telling you it's coming.

00:09:24.302 --> 00:09:48.988
Get ready, because we're seeing something that has to happen so that the Lord Jesus Christ is coming back.

00:09:48.989 --> 00:09:54.432
We're in that last generation; we are the generation that will not taste death.

00:09:54.433 --> 00:10:00.348
We are the generation that will experience the great outpouring, a spiritual awakening.

00:10:00.349 --> 00:10:06.062
Billie said, 'Brandon, it's bigger than a revival.'Because I said, 'A revival is coming, Mrs.

00:10:06.063 --> 00:10:49.463
Billie.'And she said, 'No, an awakening unto God is coming.'Billie said, 'An awakening unto God is a generation of people who are filled with and controlled by the Holy Spirit.'Diana's going to look that up for us so I can get it precise.

00:10:49.464 --> 00:10:56.705
Where did that squirrel go? Oh, he dropped the french fry on the limb up there.

00:10:56.706 --> 00:11:01.733
He's looking at me going, 'What is he doing down there?'He doesn't trust me; he's freaking out.

00:11:01.734 --> 00:11:10.521
Everybody want to say hi to Braden? There's my boy; that's Braden. He's the one that does the videos for you all the time.

00:11:10.522 --> 00:11:15.479
I'd show you my Paisley, but I still keep her secret right now because she's so young.

00:11:15.480 --> 00:11:37.177
Megan's in the back seat laying down. She just got her belly full of a hamburger.

00:11:37.178 --> 00:11:51.220
An awakening is when God sovereignly pours out his spirit and it impacts a culture. That is what happened during the Jesus Revolution.

00:11:51.221 --> 00:12:09.723
A revival, on the other hand, is what the church most experiences; it's when the church comes back to life and returns to passion.

00:12:09.724 --> 00:12:14.225
America needs a spiritual awakening, but the church needs a revival.

00:12:14.226 --> 00:12:23.308
It's a bigger impact. Just like she was talking about the Welsh Revival.

00:12:23.309 --> 00:12:49.182
In the Welsh Revival, they had to retrain the mules for the miners because they were so used to being spoken to with profanity that when the fire of God showed up and changed them, they had to retrain those donkeys because they didn't know how to do the commands without profanity.

00:12:49.183 --> 00:14:00.294
The revival changes you from the inside out. The Lord's going to change you from the inside out; he will deliver you from generational curses.

00:14:00.295 --> 00:14:19.697
Abraham was a father of many nations. It was a generational thing.

00:14:19.698 --> 00:14:35.026
What John Bevere said he called his rabbi friend, and his rabbi friend was telling him that it was 'I'll bless you,'and he repeats it three times in that Bible verse.

00:14:35.027 --> 00:14:43.877
It was generational, changing your bloodline in the spirit realm.

00:14:43.878 --> 00:15:00.265
We are changing what you thought—well, 'My dad was a drunkard, and his dad was a drunkard.'It will stop with me.

00:15:00.266 --> 00:15:11.237
I will be the one in my generation that will break the family curses.

00:15:11.238 --> 00:15:22.860
As for me and my house, we will serve the Lord. We're barrier breakers.

00:15:22.861 --> 00:15:29.755
I'm telling you, it's time to look up, for our redemption is drawing nigh. 2025 will be a year of great outpouring.

00:15:29.756 --> 00:16:05.393
We're going to start to see a major turnaround starting, I believe, from Rosh Hashanah to Rosh Hashanah.

00:16:05.394 --> 00:16:33.596
The Lord said this to me: 'Brandon, we're going to start to see a major turnaround of things.'We see the first fruits of President Trump coming on the scene and changing things for the better.

00:16:33.597 --> 00:16:37.838
What the devil meant for bad, God's going to turn it around for good.

00:16:37.839 --> 00:16:54.078
In this next four years until the next Shmita cycle, we have a window to bring in the lost.

00:16:54.079 --> 00:17:14.759
Even if it's four years until the next Shmita cycle, we have a great opportunity to go home in the Rapture of the church by 2028.

00:17:14.760 --> 00:17:21.838
The Tribulation will kick off at the next Shmita cycle; it will be a seven-year window of tribulation.

00:17:21.839 --> 00:17:43.153
We would start to see this temple being built, like the Lord told me—that Trump would have a hand in bringing in the peace accord with Saudi Arabia so that they can build the Third Temple.

00:17:43.154 --> 00:18:09.460
What will we do with what God has given us? Especially you pastors: have a church ready for the Holy Spirit to move in.

00:18:09.461 --> 00:19:31.211
Are you all in? Have you said, 'Yes, Lord, here am I, use me'? Diana and I are saying, 'Yes, here am I, Lord, use us.'If he can use me, folks, he can use you.

00:19:31.212 --> 00:19:57.714
I was just a janitor. I cleaned floors for hours and I just said, 'God, use me.

00:19:57.715 --> 00:20:18.678
Send me to the nations.'Braden was a little boy; I'd sit him on my lap and we'd pray in the Holy Spirit.

00:20:18.679 --> 00:20:53.868
We have a compassion for the lost. He will do something with those that are hungry. Just sell out today.

00:20:53.869 --> 00:21:52.131
Never lose that childlike expectation, kind of like on Christmas morning, that Daddy's going to come through. He gives us an expected end; he has good things for us.

00:21:52.132 --> 00:22:10.397
I think a lot of times people get weary in well-doing and you lose that sense of awe, like John Bevere was talking about in his book today.

00:22:10.398 --> 00:22:23.419
Don't lose your awe for him because he's worthy of it all. All this other crap is just what it is.

00:22:23.420 --> 00:22:59.232
We just wanted to encourage y'all today. We were just sitting here looking at the squirrel. I saw the squirrel and his french fry he left up there.

00:22:59.233 --> 00:23:22.116
I wanted to be like Bob Ross and say, 'Hey, little peanut-in-the-pocket squirrel, how are you doing, little buddy?'We sit out here in the car because Megan doesn't like to get out much.

00:23:22.117 --> 00:23:43.208
We got Starlink up here, so we are able to do our internet and download our videos through our mobile command center.

00:23:43.209 --> 00:24:34.879
Braden got an Apple computer; we're so thankful for the person that sowed that to him.

00:24:34.880 --> 00:25:31.439
We're humbled. Never take for granted the small things. My heart's just full. We believe that Megan's going to be completely healed.

00:25:31.440 --> 00:25:47.599
You know, he said, 'Do you trust me?'If anything was to happen with Diana and me, it will help take care of her when we're gone.

00:25:47.600 --> 00:27:06.366
And those are the things we have to say: 'Do we trust him?'I say, 'Lord, I believe, but help my unbelief,'because right now I'm weak and having a hard time because I see my daughter is still overcoming.

00:27:06.367 --> 00:29:04.540
You can't let fear steal that peace. Diana doesn't have a problem with her weight; she's always Steady Eddie.

00:29:04.541 --> 00:29:34.875
Is our peanut-in-the-pocket squirrel up there again? He's looking at us like, 'Go away, dude.'Well, you can look around; there's a nice Olive Garden over there.

00:29:34.876 --> 00:33:46.792
Father, I thank you for every single one of these people. We call their marriages restored.

00:33:46.793 --> 00:34:48.581
